Moreover, being a chain the price for the meal remains contained, despite the area in which it is located !! Prices vary between 8 and 18 $, per person, based on the menu required. The place is quite clean, there are many seats, although it is difficult to find a free "hole" around lunchtime and around dinner time! I highly recommend trying it at least once as the staff is courteous and very quick to prepare the requested dish in front of you, the ingredients are fresh and good. Using high-quality raw ingredients, classic cooking techniques, and distinctive interior design, we brought features from the realm of fine dining to the world of quick-service restaurants.  Over 23 years later, our devotion to seeking out the very best ingredients we can--raised with respect for animals, farmers, and the environment--remains at the core of our commitment to Food With Integrity.
